<li><a href="http://www.revneal.org/Writings/WesArmin.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.revneal.org/Writings/WesArmin.htm" rel="nofollow">Wesleyan Theology: Arminianism</a> by Gregory S. Neal (from a Methodist perspective)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/01740c.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/01740c.htm" rel="nofollow">Arminianism</a> from the <a href="/wiki/Catholic_Encyclopedia" title="Catholic Encyclopedia">Catholic Encyclopedia</a></li>
